=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Bayview Luxury Apartments - Palm Tree Logo\" \/>        <\/div>\n        \n        \n        <h2>Our Locations <\/h2>\n\n                <p class='description'>Perched high above Torquay\u2019s seafront, this contemporary collection of apartments treats its guests to sweeping views across the shimmering bay.<\/p>\n        \n    <\/div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"locations-display--inner\">\n\n\n        \n        \n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/locations\/flat-7\/\" class='locations-display--link' data-router-disabled>\n            <div class=\"locations-display--item\">\n                <div class=\"locations-display--item__inner\">\n\n                    <div class=\"locations-display--item-image\">\n                        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/3c6edd1e-1491-427c-baca-9af0dda47ce0-2.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" \/>                    <\/div>\n\n\n\n                                        <div class=\"locations-display--item--title\">\n                        <h4>Flat 7<\/h4>\n                        <h6>Vernon Court, Torquay<\/h6>\n                        <p>See more<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n\n        \n        \n        \n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/locations\/flat-8\/\" class='locations-display--link' data-router-disabled>\n            <div class=\"locations-display--item\">\n                <div class=\"locations-display--item__inner\">\n\n                    <div class=\"locations-display--item-image\">\n                        <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Bayview - Flat 8 torquay location\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794.jpeg 2000w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794-1024x682.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794-768x512.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/190339794-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" \/>                    <\/div>\n\n\n\n                                        <div class=\"locations-display--item--title\">\n                        <h4>Flat 8<\/h4>\n                        <h6>Vernon Court, Torquay<\/h6>\n                        <p>See more<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n\n        \n        \n\n\n\n    <\/div>\n\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"FeatureSection\" id=\"FeatureSection-block_63dccde64ba52\">\n    <div class=\"inner-feature-section\">\n                <div class=\"ifs-image\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_532124822.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_532124822.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_532124822-250x300.jpg 250w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_532124822-853x1024.jpg 853w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_532124822-768x922.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"ifs-text-item\">\n            <div class=\"ifs-item-inner\">\n                                <h2 class='ifs-title'>Open plan living<\/h2>\n                                                <div class=\"ifs-text-area\">\n                    \n                                        <p>Open plan living means you can unwind together after a busy day exploring the English Riviera, and we love the way these apartments are flooded with natural light to bring the outdoors in. Just imagine waking up, popping the coffee on and watching the waves dancing in the bay below\u2026 <\/p>\n                    \n                    \n                                        <p>Bayview Apartments are all about taking time out and making memories together. You\u2019ll have plenty of space to cook your favourite family meals, before cosying up in the living space to watch the latest film on Netflix or Disney+. <\/p>\n                    \n                                    <\/div>\n                \n                \n\n                            <\/div>\n\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"FeatureSection\" id=\"FeatureSection-block_63dccd8c4ba50\">\n    <div class=\"inner-feature-section\">\n                <div class=\"ifs-image\">\n            <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/bayviewholidayapartments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/02\/AdobeStock_447461065-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"ifs-text-item\">\n            <div class=\"ifs-item-inner\">\n                                <h2 class='ifs-title'>Explore the bay<\/h2>\n                                                <div class=\"ifs-text-area\">\n                    \n                                        <p>When you\u2019re ready for a day\u2019s exploring, you\u2019ll find Torquay\u2019s bustling town centre just a short walk away. Indulge in a spot of souvenir shopping by the harbour, treat yourselves to a picnic or just grab an afternoon tea and watch the world go by. \r\n<\/p>\n                    \n                    \n                                        <p>If that sandy beach looks tempting when you\u2019re taking in those views, you\u2019ll be just a leisurely stroll from the sands below. That means you can check the tide and gather the clan to enjoy as much time as possible on that award-winning stretch of sand. The beach is manned by a lifeguard during high season, and you\u2019ll find cafes and restaurants just moments away for those big appetites. <\/p>\n                    \n                    \n                                        <p>Just behind Torre Abbey Sands, the wide open space of Torre Abbey Meadows is great fun for visitors of all ages. While away an afternoon kicking a ball with the kids, try your hand at crazy golf or wander the mini maze. <\/p>\n                    \n                                    <\/div>\n                \n                \n\n                            <\/div>\n\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v21.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/